options.Name: Rockpea
options.Description: This is a fish. In Asterleeds, some fish have delicious meat and are often made into tasty seafood dishes. Of course, there are also some highly ornamental fish, so Guild merchants also collect them.
options.Description2: It is said that some fishing enthusiasts even dismantle their houses just to build a large aquarium to display and show off their collection of these treasures.
